  "title": "6 months Admin Assistant ($2000) #HJOT",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are hiring Temporary Administrative Assistants to be outsourced to our client from a reputable healthcare organization.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Apply now!</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Receive non-stock goods in system</li>\n  <li>Check and verify goods received from vendors</li>\n  <li>Submit and endorse invoices</li>\n  <li>Deliver goods to respective operating rooms and cabinets</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Effective communication skills</li>\n  <li>Able to multi-task</li>\n  <li>Able to commit for minimum 6 months</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>All interested candidates are invited to email your resume in MS Word format to:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>healthscience@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please include your full working experience, education background, notice period, and expected salary.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Kennice Aw</p>\n<p>Outsourcing Team</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret to inform that only suitable candidates will be shortlisted for an interview.]</p>",
